[[Image:Riga DeutscheBotschaft.jpg|thumb|250px|right| The [[Germany|German]] embassy in [[Riga]]]]A foreign '''embassy''' is the official office of one [[country]] in the [[Capital (city)|capital]] of another country. It is where the [[ambassador]] (representative) of the home country works and it is where most of the [[communication]] (talk) between the two [[governments]] happen.


